	•	Notifications system

⸻

💡 Key Concepts Demonstrated
	•	DOM manipulation
	•	Event handling
	•	Data visualization
	•	Responsive UI design
	•	Single Page Application (SPA) behavior
	•	Theme management using CSS variables

